{"tid":1325392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［歷史教訓]陣型係好重要","createTime":"2019-07-17T00:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T11:27:13.000Z","uid":30856,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2cf6ee26f1daf7558b1f7a82e5bb09667b56cf","tid":1325392,"uid":30856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:52:26.000Z","msg":"早兩日睇左套戲 套戲個名叫 patriot<br />\n係講美國獨立戰爭既<br />\n當中有一幕係英軍發炮炸美軍<br />\n美軍因爲個陣容太密集 比人炸到仆街<br />\n我諗左陣 同睇電視見到你地佈防頂催淚彈既企位好有關係<br />\n試諗下 如果你地企得太密集 我發炮都想炸你個位啦<br />\n<br />\n另外 美軍將一隊英軍拉去自己主力前面圍毆既一幕都好相似<br />\n<br />\n我覺得你地應該分散少少咁企 唔好迫哂係前面<br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n有需要時再一齊向前壓會有衝擊力<br />\n狗推進時需要更大縱深 容易over extand被分割包圍<br />\n催淚彈難搵target 而且救火隊更易移向目標 唔會比人阻住<br />\n更多人可以睇清楚距離 唔會tk自己前線<br />\n缺點：<br />\n需要更大既戰場<br />\n<br />\n利申：純鍵戰 冇參與過任何示威遊行"},{"pid":"8a1fce4b6432ee98bcd35e03d2a5d07b1749cbd1","tid":1325392,"uid":30856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:01:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9da42ed8e1ff5c3ce1c4f3988bed2e7e052452db","tid":1325392,"uid":30856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fab5277c014f43c193545c89b6827fb2a6f256","tid":1325392,"uid":30856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:28:00.000Z","msg":"希望大家討論下"},{"pid":"e59b3331f53a967b2035c64fd932690ddc1f1617","tid":1325392,"uid":30856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:30:51.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post冇人理"},{"pid":"df82f49d9ae07b1ad1ad01d813086d0d3e347c3b","tid":1325392,"uid":30856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5e1ead67200946153af3ab2d741e553298f984","tid":1325392,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:34:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"419cf948c2a7467294a4c5675b35de045